DHFWS Birbhum Recruitment 2025 - Apply Online for Phlebotomist Posts
Harshitha / All Government Jobs / Aug 06, 2025, 14:40 IST
 National Health Mission
 1 Jobs |  Posted On : 06-Aug-2025 |  West Bengal |  Salary : 5,500 to 5,500




FOLLOW

The District Health and Family Welfare Society Birbhum (DHFWS Birbhum) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 01 Phlebotomist Posts. Interested and eligible candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their Diploma, 12th can apply for the DHFWS Birbhum Recruitment 2025. The interested applicants can apply in online mode. Here we have mentioned the education details, age limit, selection process, application fee, salary, and how to apply for these posts before the deadline. The application dates have already begun.




If you are more interested in Government Jobs, candidates can also apply for jobs in West Bengal.

DHFWS Birbhum Recruitment 2025 Eligibility Criteria:
Name of the Posts	Vacancies	Education
Phlebotomist	01	Diploma, 12th

DHFWS Birbhum Recruitment 2025 Age Limit:

The minimum age limit: 18 Years.
The maximum age limit: 50 Years.
Age relaxation is based on the Organisation's norms.

DHFWS Birbhum Recruitment 2025 Selection Process:

The selection process is based on the interview.

DHFWS Birbhum Recruitment 2025 Application Fee:

There is no application fee.

DHFWS Birbhum Recruitment 2025 Pay Scale:

The basic pay: Rs. 5,500/- per month.
How to Apply for the DHFWS Birbhum Recruitment 2025:
Go to the official website.
Visit the DHFWS Birbhum Recruitment 2025 notification.
Read the instructions carefully and check the eligibility criteria.
Fill out the application form without any mistakes.
Pay the application form without any mistakes.
Attach the required documents to the filled application form.
Submit the filled application form before the last date.
Download & take a printout of the filled application form for further use.

Important Dates:

Starting date	01-07-2025
Closing date	14-08-2025
